te>第一次影星。 有無師兄可以俾啲意見我。<br />\n求評<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/090859_29061b1b06033132adb0fdfe0b3aeb0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F090859_29061b1b06033132adb0fdfe0b3aeb0c.png&h=022bc797&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>星星嗰張可以加前景<br />\n顯得星嘅宏偉<br />\n<br />\n其他好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n你依家個張只係一點點嘅星<br />\n加前景令張相多d 變化<br />\n可以crop 走左下角的飛機光影<br />\n略嫌有少少over saturation<br />\n如果有tele lens<br />\n可以影到 orion nebula <br />\n依家主體係Orion <br />\n不妨rotate 下張相  令orion 佔多d area<br />\nkeep it up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:49:15.000Z","msg":"Thanks ching. <br />\n真係吾識汁星空嘅相。 <br />\n點樣可以令到個orion 個幾粒星突出啲？"},{"pid":"e49831ff8b33254b22eb6e7e0896b709a45a3d99","tid":1044381,"uid":216742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52ad377b1705a5dde703ec41db60d8bbc305f56c","tid":1044381,"uid":28515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e5eccd42a449007617c63b3d52f6c16e7f7ae8b","tid":1044381,"uid":216742,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"第一次影星。 有無師兄可以俾啲意見我。<br />\n求評<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/090859_29061b1b06033132adb0fdfe0b3aeb0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F090859_29061b1b06033132adb0fdfe0b3aeb0c.png&h=022bc797&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/090905_ff3c4cad261556960aaa0ddc0db714fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F090905_ff3c4c